        <div class="top-title">
            <h2>
                Osaka, Japan's vibrant metropolis, is a fusion of historical treasures and modern entertainment.
                Our guide explores the essential activities that make Osaka a captivating destination.
            </h2>
        </div>
        <p class="article-text">
            Osaka is celebrated for its lively streets, historical landmarks, and gastronomic delights. As Japan's third-largest city, it offers a unique blend of culture, history, and entertainment. From the majestic Osaka Castle to the futuristic Umeda Sky Building, this guide to the top ten things to do in Osaka promises an enriching journey through the heart of Kansai.
        </p>
        <div class="title article-text" id="osakaCastle">
            <h2>
                Exploring Osaka Castle
            </h2>
        </div>
        <p class="article-text">
            The iconic Osaka Castle is a testament to Japan's rich history and architectural beauty. Visitors can explore its museum, which houses artifacts related to the castle's history, and enjoy breathtaking views from its top. Nishinomaru Park, a haven of tranquility, becomes especially enchanting during cherry blossom season and during the autumn period.
            <br><br>
            Tip: Visiting during February? Make sure to visit the Castle's Plum Grove! It contains more than 1,200 trees of over 100 varieties of plum blossom and they produce a heavenly scent when they're in bloom.
        </p>
        <div class="block-quote">
            <p>
                <a href="https://affiliate.klook.com/redirect?aid=38574&aff_adid=825574&k_site=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.klook.com%2Factivity%2F30110-osaka-castle-ticket%2F" target="_blank">Book your ticket here</a> for the Osaka Castle Museum (¥600)
            </p>
        </div>
        <img src="{{ asset('/assets/img/osaka.jpg') }}" class="article-image" alt="Osaka Castle">
        <figcaption class="caption-text">
            Osaka Castle © Japan Guide
        </figcaption>
        <div class="title article-text" id="universalStudiosJapan">
            <h2>
                Universal Studios Japan
            </h2>
        </div>
        <p class="article-text">
            Universal Studios Japan brings to life your favorite films and franchises with exhilarating rides and shows. Highlights include Super Nintendo World, Wizarding World of Harry Potter and the Minion Park. Seasonal events add extra magic, making every visit unforgettable.
            <br><br>
            Make sure to book your tickets in advance (a month ahead in peak season just to be safe!) for the park. Once you are in the park and your ticket has been activated, you can select a timed entry for Super Nintendo World and the Wizarding World of Harry Potter.
        </p>
        <div class="block-quote">
            <p>
                <a href="https://affiliate.klook.com/redirect?aid=38574&aff_adid=825574&k_site=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.klook.com%2Factivity%2F46604-universal-studios-japan-e-ticket-osaka-qr-code-direct-entry%2F%3Fspm%3DSearchResult.SearchResult_LIST%26clickId%3Dfaad429929" target="_blank">Book your ticket here</a> for Universal Studios Japan. - 1 Day USJ Pass costs from ¥8,600 to ¥10,900 (higher prices tend to be on weekends and public holidays, the cheapest price is usually Tuesday/Wednesday/Thursday)
            </p>
        </div>
        <img src="{{ asset('/assets/img/universalstudios1.jpg') }}" class="article-image-three" alt="Universal Studios - Super Nintendo World">
        <img src="{{ asset('/assets/img/universalstudios2.jpg') }}" class="article-image-three-alt" alt="Universal Studios">
        <img src="{{ asset('/assets/img/universalstudios3.jpg') }}" class="article-image-three-alt" alt="Universal Studios - Wizarding World of Harry Potter">
