            <h2>
                Namba Yasaka Shrine: A Hidden Gem
            </h2>
        </div>
        <p class="article-text">
            Namba Yasaka Shrine, with its unique lion head stage, is a spiritual oasis in the midst of urban hustle. This lesser-known shrine offers a peaceful environment for reflection and is known for its distinctive architecture, making it a fascinating visit for those looking to explore Osaka's spiritual side.
        </p>
        <img src="{{ asset('/assets/img/nambayasaka.jpg') }}" class="article-image" alt="Namba Yasaka Shrine">
        <figcaption class="caption-text">
            Namba Yasaka Shrine © Japan Guide
        </figcaption>
